    "## Section 2: Concept 1 - Change Types (Standard, Normal, Emergency)\n",
    "\n",
    "Not all changes are created equal. We classify changes into 3 types:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Standard Changes** (pre-approved, low-risk):\n",
    "- SSL certificate renewal\n",
    "- Security patch installation\n",
    "- Log retention config update\n",
    "- Auto-approved, deploy immediately\n",
    "\n",
    "**Normal Changes** (requires approval):\n",
    "- Embedding model upgrades\n",
    "- New data source addition\n",
    "- Retrieval strategy changes\n",
    "- Manager or CAB approval (1-3 days)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Emergency Changes** (critical):\n",
    "- Zero-day vulnerability patches\n",
    "- Production outage fixes\n",
    "- Data breach mitigation\n",
    "- CISO + VP Engineering approval (<2 hours)"
