    "## Section 3: Concept 2 - Approval Routing (Who Approves What)\n",
    "\n",
    "Based on change type and risk level, changes are routed to appropriate approvers:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Approval Matrix:**\n",
    "- Standard + Low Risk → Auto-approved\n",
    "- Normal + Low/Medium Risk → Manager (1 business day SLA)\n",
    "- Normal + High Risk → CAB (3 business days SLA)\n",
    "- Emergency + Any Risk → CISO + VP Engineering (2 hours SLA)\n",
    "\n",
    "**CAB Members:**\n",
    "1. Chief Architect (technical feasibility)\n",
    "2. Head of Security (security impact)\n",
    "3. Compliance Officer (regulatory impact)\n",
    "4. Lead DevOps Engineer (operational impact)\n",
    "5. Business Representative (user impact)\n",
    "6. Finance Representative (financial impact)\n",
    "7. Legal Representative (contract compliance)"
   ]
